{"tid":2433916,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"元朗男趴車頭玩命 司機乘客狂笑推行500米","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T08:46:24.000Z","uid":100150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2cd9b7eea7c23eda18d563322bdd193e17b204","tid":2433916,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:49:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ff19h3MQEvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fff19h3MQEvI&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUhT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=8e22d188\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ff19h3MQEvI</a><br />\n周四（4日）網上流傳一條長約40秒的瘋狂駕駛片段。片中一名男子竟趴在私家車車頭位置，司機其後開車，將趴在車頭的男子推行逾500米，非常牙煙。《蘋果》現就事件向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://external-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQFjmCiXnQ2aPEAk&amp;w=500&amp;h=261&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvlOLVLkad10gG97qelYXVN2RqwU%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F03-05-2021%2Ft_310e54a7cd9f4964827988497f4af9b5_name_000000_0134321_meitu_2.jpg&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;_nc_cb=1&amp;_nc_hash=AQEdLFXmXntz3lga\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQFjmCiXnQ2aPEAk%26w%3D500%26h%3D261%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fhk.appledaily.com%252Fresizer%252FvlOLVLkad10gG97qelYXVN2RqwU%253D%252F1920x1080%252Ffilters%253Aquality%2528100%2529%252Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%252F03-05-2021%252Ft_310e54a7cd9f4964827988497f4af9b5_name_000000_0134321_meitu_2.jpg%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26_nc_cb%3D1%26_nc_hash%3DAQEdLFXmXntz3lga&h=2802f2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片段開首時，一名身穿風褸的男子已趴在私家車車頭位置，當時車內傳出一把女子聲音：「黐線。咪玩啦」，但司機竟未有理會，更不斷爆粗瘋狂大笑，並將風褸男由元朗媽橫路及屏會街交界開始，一直向前推行，當時私家車兩旁有多架車輛駛經，驚險萬分。司機初時更意圖將車駛上橋，但被車上的女乘客喝斥，他才將私家車停在550米外的朗庭園外。<br />\n<br />\n有關片段未有標明事發時間，事後分別被放到fb及YouTube廣傳，有網民指二人的行為非常危險，「模仿P牌女車頭載客事件？」、「人有病有得醫，人儍想醫都難」、「早登極樂」、「成個傻仔」，呼籲所有司機切勿貪圖一時快感，切勿模仿。<br />\n<br />\n上月5日晚上，元朗曾發生瘋狂駕駛事件，一輛私家車在教育路撞向一輛停泊在前面的客貨車車尾，其後倒車意圖駛離現場。客貨車司機下車站在私家車車頭拍攝車牌，其間私家車竟撞向客貨車司機，客貨車司機趴在私家車車頭阻止，竟遭私家車推行120米拋落地。私家車逃去後在兩公里外的十八鄉迴旋處失事，女司機逃去無蹤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tKrmatGSUTJXJF-BHsEJPJBf7s0=/802x420/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LEIN7TXUXBBKZB376ZZ6JLAHAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtKrmatGSUTJXJF-BHsEJPJBf7s0%3D%2F802x420%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLEIN7TXUXBBKZB376ZZ6JLAHAY.jpg&h=fbcdd8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周四（4日）網上流傳一條長約40秒的瘋狂駕駛片段。片中一名男子竟趴在私家車車頭位置，司機其後開車，將趴在車頭的男子推行逾500米，非常牙煙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Es7XPkjfSUOCTNMXTh9bfR5yGvc=/802x470/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/64NNFY5ORJBFPFJKRMQEBBEJNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEs7XPkjfSUOCTNMXTh9bfR5yGvc%3D%2F802x470%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F64NNFY5ORJBFPFJKRMQEBBEJNM.jpg&h=d7d63a92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zyH2tDgIDfZ5aaC2Bb8MSRn0SWs=/802x454/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KRJNITYHP5CI7DN42KPKQH35QY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzyH2tDgIDfZ5aaC2Bb8MSRn0SWs%3D%2F802x454%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKRJNITYHP5CI7DN42KPKQH35QY.jpg&h=f1c02cfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d24599d1adf2301cdcdb72cbdd3c0bf3c51db44","tid":2433916,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"望唔到車前狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚危險"},{"pid":"0ff2abd2edf7a09446538b65170ca5b5d975d085","tid":2433916,"uid":301406,"like":0,"dislik